      },
      "dialogue": [
        "The best way to explain a Caucus-race is to do it!",
        "First, mark out a race-course, in a sort of circle.",
        "Then all the party were placed along the course, here and there.",
        "Everybody has won, and all must have prizes!",
        "The key awaits at the center. Run the race to claim it!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Mouse",
      "model_id": "mouse",
      "position": {
        "x": -5,
        "y": 2,
        "z": -5
      },
      "dialogue": [
        "I'll soon make you dry enough with the driest thing I know!",
        "Mine is a long and a sad tale!",
        "It IS a long tail, certainly, but why do you call it sad?",
        "Follow the circular path - all winners get prizes!"
      ]
    },
